<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1882004/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            中国上下五千年的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2062333">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2062333/" class="title-link">贯穿五千年的故事书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2062333"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/baiyanhuang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2984774-20.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/baiyanhuang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">西山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-07"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-07 18:21:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2062333_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    确切的讲，这不是一本历史书，而是一本故事书，他把中国几千年来发生的一些大事，趣事，有意义的事汇集在一个个小故事里呈现出来，把这些无论是你听到过的，还是没听到过的小故事用一条时间的长线串联起来。   读完这本书前后用了半年多吧，一般都是睡前读个一两篇，很有意思...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2062333_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2062333_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5233681">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5233681/" class="title-link">观感</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5233681"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/57324338/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u57324338-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57324338/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">晓晗</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-28"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-28 11:32:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5233681_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是我较早时读的一本书，应该算是科普读物。这本书大概叙述了中国历史，条理清楚。记叙了各个年份发生的大事。语言浅显易懂，偶尔还配以插图，图文并茂。适合历史入门者阅读，对历史知识的普及很有帮助。尤其是青少年，读完此书可对中国历史有基本的认识。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5233681_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5233681_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










